title: There are 1440 unique minority-owned vendors in Dallas County
text:
There are 1440 unique minority-owned vendors in Dallas County

according to the Texas Comptroller vendors list







545 listed as Black-owned


238 listed as Asian-owned


274 listed as Hispanic-owned


23 listed as Native American-owned


349 listed as Women-owned


11 listed as owned by a Service Disabled Veteran of 20% or more
